definitions.definition: A market town and civil parish with a town council in Buckinghamshire , England , previously in Chiltern district ( OS grid ref SP9501 ) .
An unincorporated community in the town of Harrisville , Cheshire County , New Hampshire , United States . See Chesham, New Hampshire on  Wikipedia. Wikipedia
